1999-03-01 Monday 22:26  gabriel

	* CREDITS (1.10), src/hpt.c (1.19), src/scan.c (1.44), src/toss.c
	(1.84): Mon Mar  1 22:00   Gabriel Plutzar + included support for
	generic new keyword for LogLevels   * LogLevels <string>     You
	can specify all Loglevels you want in your log	   Default is
	123456789, use 23456789 if you don't want all the IDLE	   sessions
	in your logfile (eg when you start hpt once a minute)	+ Major
	Changes in log.c & log.h were necessary to supress unwanted	log
	file entries in IDLE only hpt sessions (like regularily scanning   
	 the netmail area without something happening worth logging)   +
	Changes to the code to force all unneeded log entries to loglevel 1

