1999-02-20 Saturday 20:21  tobi

	* h/fcommon.h (1.14, hpt-0_26), src/fcommon.c (1.19), src/hpt.c
	(1.17), src/scanarea.c (1.23, hpt-0_26), src/toss.c (1.80): + Added
	support for QQQ files. If found in the tempOutbound, they will be  
	packed into the outgoing arcmail bundle. This is useful if you use 
	 CFRoute: You can point CFRoutes tempOutbound to the fidoconfig
	tempOut,   in order to pack netmail into arcmail bundles.  + Added
	support for packet forwarding. See the fidoconfig manual for  
	information.

