1999-01-27 Wednesday 12:21  tobi

	* src/: dupe.c (1.13), toss.c (1.68): - Fixed non-standard
	preprocessor directives.    Hey, everybody: YOU MUST PUT THE # HASH
	MARK FOR A PREPROCESSOR DIRECTIVE    TO THE VERY FRIST COLUMN OF
	THE SOURCE CODE!. I.e., use
	
	#ifdef blah
	
	  and NOT
	
	  #ifdef blah
	
	  !!!

