1998-10-12 Monday 10:22  tobi

	* src/seenby.c (1.2): Removed the inline operator before the
	compare functions for two reasons: #1: The GNU compiler cannot
	handle function pointers to inline functions,	  so the compare
	function would not be inlined anyway #2: AIX xlC does not
	understand it.

